Class ConditionAttributeDelta

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.spe.pricing.transactiondata.calctrace.ConditionAttributeDelta
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ConditionAttributeDelta
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is used for the calculation trace of the User Exits. It stores a condition attribute before and after the call of a user exit, for example exchange rate or condition inactive flag.
